headline: 3 Monster Dividend Stocks to Hold for the Next 10 Years
summary: With yields as high as 6.7%, these three income stocks are all monsters in the markets they serve.  With a Dividend King leading the way, even conservative investors will find these three stocks worth owning for decades to come.  Don't give up on dividend stocks, though, because you can still find some great options if you dig a little.
